{
  "logNo": "222710134249",
  "title": "큰 사고가 아닌 것 같았는데, 이상하게도 교통사고 후유증이 심해요",
  "addDate": "2022. 4. 24.",
  "categoryNo": "12",
  "parentCategoryNo": "7",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=222710134249",
  "html_size": 214731,
  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a5d18d5e-5b38-46d0-abf9-0e914a965c6f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0105869c-d240-4075-b5cf-af12f459d3e5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f0192626-f333-4d3b-b818-4de4334cd23f\">여러분은 교통사고를 경험해본적이 있나요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7aa9b560-bb14-4f62-8728-253107d5bdbd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ffd7b00c-f2d8-464e-a1fe-c366585ef10b\">차량이 뒤집히고, 승용차가 반으로 쪼그라들 정도의 큰 사고는 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-164c17a3-8d17-4598-8cf1-9b80aba570b5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c9b37588-61ea-4fb7-95c0-dfa69503aa30\">탑승자의 목숨을 위태롭게 하거나 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-47d36856-957b-46f5-96f2-8f9b01d2781d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0a914b1d-bf1d-4c13-bbbd-11b9f29b18ec\">골절 및 자상(예리한 물체 등에 살이 깊이 패이는 상처) 등이 발생해 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-543ce945-215f-4c4b-8602-95f93d30323c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-96e60ec9-0241-4064-8ec7-573428d89e50\">큰 후유증이 남을 수 있다고 여겨집니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a562492f-04a8-461e-b396-77c077331c1a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a562492f-04a8-461e-b396-77c077331c1a\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA0MjRfMjg2/MDAxNjUwODAwODIwNzg1.n77f17Jl7xSezyctAPxG-dY0zdMeSbVOw0C14b8KIqUg.nzRIT6H635aUn6bzrBJdmzCLnNssk9MmFNvLPdDPnsYg.JPEG.isuhani/TA1.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"930\", \"originalHeight\" : \"699\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA0MjRfMjg2/MDAxNjUwODAwODIwNzg1.n77f17Jl7xSezyctAPxG-dY0zdMeSbVOw0C14b8KIqUg.nzRIT6H635aUn6bzrBJdmzCLnNssk9MmFNvLPdDPnsYg.JPEG.isuhani/TA1.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA0MjRfMjg2/MDAxNjUwODAwODIwNzg1.n77f17Jl7xSezyctAPxG-dY0zdMeSbVOw0C14b8KIqUg.nzRIT6H635aUn6bzrBJdmzCLnNssk9MmFNvLPdDPnsYg.JPEG.isuhani/TA1.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"375\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-984ec7e7-5de2-4f72-892b-99348ea067a1\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8e91bd92-08ec-478b-b221-5a4e198fcd5a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-29127ab8-2be9-4a48-bebd-f2260899d8d9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-72d9c5af-f906-4f16-8cdb-a00056786614\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7fce8982-ad78-45ba-b20b-fc41330e2292\">그렇지만, 심각한 교통사고는 흔치 않죠. 뉴스 및 미디어를 통해 접하니까 익숙해보이는거지 실제로 많이 발생하는건 아니거든요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9f93511c-6ea0-4eba-873d-4ade0f3352e2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-561e088a-b3f8-4770-a972-6120c23b0638\">대다수의 교통사고는 &#x27;접촉사고&#x27;라고 말 할 정도의 사고이거나 신체에 외상을 일으키지 않을 정도의 사고입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-057caf13-b6d7-49a3-a9e2-15800da93175\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-62098162-b84e-4aa3-b47a-3cb49b050e40\">차량끼리 접촉 혹은 충돌이 있었지만, 탑승자들은 멀쩡히 차에서 내려 시시비비를 가리고 보험사를 부르고 경찰을 부르는 등 사고 수습을 하잖아요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2c4e01c6-3051-42df-a63e-c869a145d821\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0148f66d-31c2-4614-bdb4-6cbeab795d92\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7aa8210a-8e11-45cc-be2b-acd55ba97475\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-820dbfe8-450d-40b6-8641-b7abe1eda1da\">그런데,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d9e6f849-d48b-4f66-9f77-2079b21dc855\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fdbe0e03-7f0e-4ec3-ac07-e252fe2b4f2d\">사고가 수습된 후가 문제입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-931e2068-a067-46c4-86af-ce33f1489fe3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5be959f7-5404-406c-afb8-4b9ab0d2dddc\">(물론 차에서 내리는 순간부터 뒷목을 잡거나 허리를 부여잡는 경우도 있긴 하죠. 저도 몇 번의 교통사고를 경험해봐서 사고의 충격이 의외로 크다는걸 알고 있습니다. 한 번은 병원에 1주이상 입원했던 적도 있어요)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2825ee88-51ae-41f5-9107-97b6ad942fca\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2d486a98-a623-4560-ac0b-67dcac5c679e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c057c068-d5f7-4bfb-bdc6-80b2bdfdc918\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:268px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c057c068-d5f7-4bfb-bdc6-80b2bdfdc918\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA0MjRfMjEw/MDAxNjUwODAwODQzMzMw.6e2v7g8Pp2lj5S31IIDRcLbKcKTfXRzZfhVj5F_xpTEg.ii7GR0HXpoZTUsYWrhWVcG-CwST7IOd1m1rZqrUjIKIg.JPEG.isuhani/Ta4.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"268\", \"originalHeight\" : \"188\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA0MjRfMjEw/MDAxNjUwODAwODQzMzMw.6e2v7g8Pp2lj5S31IIDRcLbKcKTfXRzZfhVj5F_xpTEg.ii7GR0HXpoZTUsYWrhWVcG-CwST7IOd1m1rZqrUjIKIg.JPEG.isuhani/Ta4.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA0MjRfMjEw/MDAxNjUwODAwODQzMzMw.6e2v7g8Pp2lj5S31IIDRcLbKcKTfXRzZfhVj5F_xpTEg.ii7GR0HXpoZTUsYWrhWVcG-CwST7IOd1m1rZqrUjIKIg.JPEG.isuhani/Ta4.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"268\" data-height=\"188\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-64b291fc-aab8-4420-a529-912839792f27\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3406f765-baeb-4451-a00a-d54557938682\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bba1ed54-2809-407b-9180-f379913b78a7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8d1c02ae-5109-40b4-aadf-c75b8fee2543\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8a9f2785-b812-4d55-ae5d-2adbb85cd714\">사고 당시에는 많이 아픈지 몰랐는데</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-27e8cc48-4a94-4ee8-a3fa-3c901b026f8c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-753102f6-7056-4df6-8375-33a2c4db3663\">하루 또는 이틀이 지난후에야 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0839a8e7-0185-4ef2-80fe-7ee255ced07a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f529890a-fb46-436a-bc55-8e91f2bb7ae2\">&#x27;허리가 뻐근해&#x27;, &#x27;목이 아프고 두통이 안없져&#x27;,  &#x27;여기저기 관절이 아프네&#x27; </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f8334d69-cf3a-4cd5-97eb-7d2ab523fb3a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6ce3a4e3-1164-46f2-923b-309975b32133\">이전과 다르게 몸이 아픈걸 느끼게 되는 분들이 적지 않다는거죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2ae446b3-10f6-4564-b261-aa08af7157c7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8bfcc253-7e2c-404f-bcf4-a1cd7bb821c8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-49b33d64-bc3f-4001-88e2-84621fc84c80\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-49b33d64-bc3f-4001-88e2-84621fc84c80\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA0MjRfMjcx/MDAxNjUwODAwODUwOTQ5.FCJDOCxWmXsVzXfVPnfz0IZtxEvP6t0yyZoMk5f2eKIg.XzCHzuJVtuXOR_6wL9n5mI7F42QtQEqSOZAoT1NQJiMg.JPEG.isuhani/TA3.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"612\", \"originalHeight\" : \"397\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA0MjRfMjcx/MDAxNjUwODAwODUwOTQ5.FCJDOCxWmXsVzXfVPnfz0IZtxEvP6t0yyZoMk5f2eKIg.XzCHzuJVtuXOR_6wL9n5mI7F42QtQEqSOZAoT1NQJiMg.JPEG.isuhani/TA3.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA0MjRfMjcx/MDAxNjUwODAwODUwOTQ5.FCJDOCxWmXsVzXfVPnfz0IZtxEvP6t0yyZoMk5f2eKIg.XzCHzuJVtuXOR_6wL9n5mI7F42QtQEqSOZAoT1NQJiMg.JPEG.isuhani/TA3.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"324\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bc1c1949-b823-4499-8ecc-61bb78c5f4a1\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f5ebdb51-2218-46a3-bd52-74942aa3218c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0df69b6f-5001-406e-a736-ddf213b3bdf7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e3113b33-a8d1-4457-88ec-41d75fe3a43a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d6d2fea5-e49a-4f30-9cb2-f2212c359c77\">왜 그럴까요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-58a235a5-7577-4a53-8f9c-4b065f5ff550\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-16bf598d-8c72-43b6-a110-13c69642c2b2\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9757b32d-e9ce-44e0-a7f3-5876b462a732\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-faf3036e-ecf1-4298-ba46-c88e35665187\">교통사고를 당하는 당사자에게는 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a2076bc3-522d-4599-869c-77e331d3c3c3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0f98913e-e5d2-4992-9d9f-1c4b623670b7\">교통사고라는 사건 자체가 아주아주 커다란 스트레스입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-48db3cad-47a5-4fb6-b45b-bf5d3404dbd6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-39b26c66-3857-4fd6-aca1-53fef3c0a2d4\">특히나 예상치 못하게 발생하는 교통사고의 경우에는 더 큰 스트레스겠죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c4af5e84-8ad7-41e3-9421-2c00792437b5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-faf82b43-2249-4580-a558-568b4c1509dd\">스트레스는 우리 몸에 여러모로 충격을 줍니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c6a52806-9b42-4656-a272-8f3b0cadd32d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-92644004-5b49-4cec-82d8-97bd5da5fdab\">자율신경계, 시상하부, 부신(adrenal) 등 신경계 및 호르몬체계에 영향을 주죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7d4f356b-e7fb-449d-a008-3d4fc6ad61e7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6ee1e083-e061-475e-8095-d159aa49ad89\">심지어 두뇌의 여러부위에 스트레스에게 줍니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aa3e767c-b5be-4916-ad94-7049a7df5e9c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5d92bc8c-4533-4223-bc57-1cd84aa2d2e1\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-abbea587-0f85-4f82-93d6-a995cc8c8d62\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-45b23d72-8b24-41c5-a992-b64973662749\">특히 섬엽Insula이라는 부위에 충격이 가는게 중요합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9cfb81e6-ae17-4ed4-85b7-a6a5822c6684\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-091caa9e-0b55-4ba2-998c-5df60ed4114f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ba89aaac-1eaf-420e-8f11-954b3e981791\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4a8aca2e-1d16-4016-b588-6274a1776c99\">섬엽Insula에 충격이 가서 신체감각에 대한 의식이 강화되어 각 신체부위의 작은 통증에도 집중하게 되어 &#x27;많이 아픈&#x27;것 처럼 인식하게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-83a2d8c8-d584-4eaf-82cb-9d0b6e23c0cd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d8df0113-de02-4e07-80d2-bb381a0f0a29\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-56e83fed-0c29-4685-8109-e7b57c624215\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c02800db-02fd-4784-9d85-a1820c9b5ca7\">&quot;섬엽Insula 의 활동성이 증가하면 아무리 작을지라도 몸에 생기는 모든 문제를 극도로 민감하게 의식하게 되는데 아주 사소한 일을 엄청나게 거대한 것으로 부풀리는 일은 그래서 생긴다. 그러므로 섬엽의 활동을 진정시키면 통증과 병에 대한 걱정을 줄이는 데 도움이 된다 - 우울할 땐 뇌 과학/앨릭스 코브/심심&quot;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dc4ea413-25d4-4ea8-b6ed-15b1e7a857dd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6817d6f4-7d1a-449f-83eb-247e54501f51\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8229b5db-557f-4504-bcc8-5146830e19e4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:295px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-8229b5db-557f-4504-bcc8-5146830e19e4\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA0MjRfMTA0/MDAxNjUwODAwODMyMjgy.qt41r7xfH83CxHTK138wzZx7CJbHFtQ8d9vbV4SXfWwg.PNWZI-p6Z0m-zWLahWvO8exAo3yVlfQ9VAJvsilL8-Yg.JPEG.isuhani/TA2.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"295\", \"originalHeight\