5-7ff9-4bec-9627-2af109176b3e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-babfe1ac-101c-4b63-92c0-60277759215d\">관절 인대의 염좌에 대한 치료</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-44bea787-1080-4a0c-bd00-84e8f8c96602\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-65bc13fa-b61e-4f4d-96a6-e2d97a7c3b59\">근육 긴장에 대한 치료</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f738ee18-a183-4e3d-90b2-e8537fbaf561\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-178a31cc-2845-4363-8132-68e3d588d1b5\">자율신경의 과활성에 대한 치료가 필요하고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-496e5817-05d6-4859-9c0b-a3417ad6573a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c65a585f-e7f7-40a4-a91d-c6f095a2e46a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f80c4b81-1aaf-4137-9c08-8783568b8cb6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1dd6afb8-18a5-4518-8c30-89ac211ee94b\">더불어 스트레스로 인한 두뇌의 기능이상에 대한 고려가 필요합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ed6f920d-9b63-4428-afd1-083820f56b24\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5b70142a-3406-4cd7-97be-06f0db39ac27\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7d8f823b-4f22-46e3-84db-23d21c009bf8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7d8f823b-4f22-46e3-84db-23d21c009bf8\", \"src\" : \"https://exploringyourmind.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-insula-found-within-the-brain.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"768\", \"originalHeight\" : \"419\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://exploringyourmind.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-insula-found-within-the-brain.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a6f4303-aaf4-410c-9ac8-b9a905bd8555\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3e1bcce4-453f-4ca9-994a-626780364c82\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6dd7b3eb-7910-44cf-8857-0bb8fa8119e2\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d0fcf37d-24fd-4853-b0dd-cb6a4cd75979\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-787a8019-e7d4-4658-b387-84486f77a218\">이수한의원에서는 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-92710559-3bae-428c-9cd2-05d93931ebac\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5d51a620-4115-42b1-b339-b235ba6c5782\">근골격계에 대한 치료와 더불어 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-pa